Name: Warehouse Tycoon
About the game: Manage your own warehouse in Warehouse Tycoon! Start from scratch + build your own shipping/receiving empire! Overcome a variety of obstacles both inside and out of the warehouse. Be sure to get the best bang for your buck because time is money! Features: • Company Van: Drive around to purchase inventory and deliver orders • Warehouse: Design your layout (place shelving, and pallets) • Inventory: Travel to cities and towns to buy inventory for your warehouse) • Laptop: Manage your warehouse right from your desk! Pay bills, check emails, and regulate inventory • Be the Boss: Wear a suit and tie
